name: Stash Ports Controller Optional
desc: 可选且谨慎：设置 mixed-port、allow-lan、bind-address 和 external-controller；若 iOS 导入失败请不要使用
category: settings
icon: https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Koolson/Qure@master/IconSet/Color/Direct.png

mixed-port: 7890
allow-lan: true
bind-address: '*'
external-controller: 127.0.0.1:9090
